<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="wreck-vt">wreck <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rek/    美 /rek/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>使失事；使遭难；损害：毁坏:</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The ship was wrecked on the rocks. 
船撞毁在礁石上。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The accident wrecked his health.
这次意外事故损坏了他的健康。</p></div></div>